'''After Effects''' d-[[aseɣẓan]] n-usudes id ẓreg [[Adobe]]. Ittaǧǧa aseqdac ad ismentel (céer) [[asemdu ameẓli|isemda imeẓliyen]] d-imrayen udlifen i yal tannalt seg yal tawsit taɣbalut. Tẓa ileqman id yefɣen seg-s ar assa, taneggarut seg-sent d Adobe After Effects CS5.5 v11.5.

== Amezruy ==

After Effects d-[[aseɣẓan]] n-usudes d-isemda uwali ig llan d-amenzu seg imrayen udlifen deg [[Aselkim n yiwen | uselkim n wemdan]]. Amecwaṛ yevda deg yiwet n tmetti tamecṭuḥt iwumi qqaṛen CoSA (The Company of Science and Art) id yuzgan di Providence addad n Rhode Island. seg asmi id sneflin aseɣẓan PACo (PICS Animation Compiler) '''Dave Herbstman''', '''Dave Simmons''' et '''Dan Wilk''' vdan di tneflit n Egg id yefkan di tagara After Effects [[Yennayer|yennayer]] usegwas 1993 i smahin di MacWorld (Boston).

iswi n useɣẓan agi d-asmentel n-imrayen i ''tiliẓṛi'' (tilivizyu) d ''sinima'' deg [[Aselkim n yiwen | uselkim n wemdan]]. Di tawala (lawan) nni tifrat n-usekker umḍin n tugna deg umḍiq imusnawen, sseqdacen arrumen yettwaxedmen iwayagi kan, yarna d-wid ɣlayen s waṭas d wid yesɛan ferru usviḍ. COSA tebwid tifrat: [[aseɣẓan]] agetferru n-usekker uvidyu, ileḥḥu ɣef [[Windows]] d [[Mac]].

Tuggdiwin deg uswir n-imusal twakecma d twafɣa llant ttwajemqent ala si tnezmart tmacint d tmeska n [[Takatut s waddadf agacuran|tkatut s waddaf agacuran]]: [[RAM (Random Access Memory]]. Aseɣẓan agi uɣent wa deffir wa ''Aldus Corporation'', sinna ''Adobe Systems Inc''. Tura After effects ittesdiwin yark aked wahilen n tseddart Adobe Creative Suite.

*1995 : lqem wis 3 - lqem tamenzut yebḍen, ig ttwasekren di ssuq ;
*1999 : lqem wis 4 - tikkelt tamenzut deg tella tasuqilt ɣer tutlayt tafṛansist ;
*2001 : lqem wis 5 - yebwid ta 3D d tinfaylin ;
*2003 : lqem wis 6 - askripti, asaraw n tira ;
*2005 : lqem wis 7 - agrudem amaynu d amarraz udlif d uqqin HDR 32 ibitten ;
*2007 : lqem wis 8 (CS3) - teskecmed isriwen n talɣiwin, d merru n tira s 3D, arnu afecku n usexweḍ ;
*2008 : lqem wis 9 (CS4) - tanezmart n-umru s-berraz imsidag xyz, asemdu n w-unuɣ amray.
*2010 : lqem wis 10 (CS5) - asaka (aɛeddi) ɣer 64 ibitten, Plug-in tiferkit.

== Tihawt ==

After Effects yesseqdac asagraw n usemnenni n iswiren iwakken ad yessuffeɣ asudes amray si tugniwin timeẓliyin. Ad naf ayagi daɣen deg aṭas iseɣẓan yecvan After Effects, amakken yella di [[Photoshop]] maca After Effects yefka iw seqdac tazemert ad iveddel iswiren deg akud, yarna s weskar ur nessengar. Neqqaṛ-as ur nessengar acku afaylu n-usenfaṛ di After Effects yesɛa ala tilɣa n-usekker aɣbalu. Iwakken ad isiḍen amray ttagara, ilaq an sɛu si tama asenfaṛ n-After Effects, si tama nniḍen tiɣbula tizedganin.
